data.description: Location, Location, Location! Close to Kilpatrick Turnpike, shopping, medical facilities and Yukon Schools. Home features a large living area with built-in book shelves, wood burning fireplace and a window open to dining room and kitchen. The kitchen has fresh painted cabinets and new lighting! The 1st floor has the primary bedroom with large closet. The stairs lead up to the 2nd floor with two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. Extra hidden room in the attic is great for a flex-room, study or storage. The large back yard features a sun room a covered patio and an out-building for great storage!
